Package org.projecthaystack.io

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HaystackToken
    Created by mgiannini on 6/6/16.
    HaystackTokenizer
    Stream based tokenizer for Haystack formats such as Zinc and Filters
    HCsvWriter
    HCsvWriter is used to write grids in comma separated values format as specified by RFC 4180.
    HGridFormat
    HGridFormat models a format used to encode/decode HGrid.
    HGridReader
    HGridReader is base class for reading grids from an input stream.
    HGridWriter
    HGridWriter is base class for writing grids to an output stream.
    HJsonWriter
    HJsonWriter is used to write grids in JavaScript Object Notation.
    HZincReader
    HZincReader reads grids using the Zinc format.
    HZincWriter
    HZincWriter is used to write grids in the Zinc format
